| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2058 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonransomware)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 50594a8f-9927-5fbc-b1c7-7410e6f6b4f0"
